ass=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 04, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wrj1665703133411.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wrj1665703133411.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wrj1665703133411.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wrj1665703133411\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"wrj1665703133411__uputreg_408517\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Copy a long integer value into the specified general variable ($1 ...\n      $99).</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"wrj1665703133411__topic_d123719e1_d123720e1_d123721e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104wrj1665703133411_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"wrj1665703133411__codeblock_pgr_tfk_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">long uputreg (shortregNbr, longvalue);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wrj1665703133411__topic_d87402e1_d87403e1_d87404e1_d87405e1_d87406e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d266194e61\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"wrj1665703133411__parml_ltz_5fk_bwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">regNbr</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Number of the Uniface general variable; must be in the range 1 to 99.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">value</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Long integer value to put into the variable. Values can be from -2147483648 to\n                  2147483647.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wrj1665703133411__topic_d87407e1_d87408e1_d87409e1_d87410e1_d87411e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d266194e90\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wrj1665703133411__p_d123737e1_d123738e1_d123739e1\">The value of the <var class=\"keyword varname\">value</var> parameter.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wrj1665703133411__topic_d87412e1_d87413e1_d87414e1_d87415e1_d87416e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d266194e102\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wrj1665703133411__d5947e20\">Library:  <span class=\"ph filepath\">yrtl</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wrj1665703133411__topic_d87417e1_d87418e1_d87419e1_d87420e1_d87421e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d266194e115\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wrj1665703133411__p_d123749e1_d123750e1_d123751e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uputreg</code> copies the specified long\n            integer value, which can range from -2147483648 to 2147483647 (or -231 to 231 -1), to\n            the Uniface general variable (also known as dollar register) with the specified number\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">regNbr</var>, which can range from 1 to 99. There is no check on the\n            validity of <var class=\"keyword varname\">regNbr</var>; if it is out of range, a crash is likely to\n            result.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104wrj1665703133411_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"wrj1665703133411__codeblock_vyr_zfk_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\n\nEXPORT long putnum ()\n{\n(void)uputreg(1, -2147483648); /* Lowest value possible */\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jqk1665703133137.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ugetreg</a><p>Get the integer value of a Uniface general variable ($1 ... $99).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kno1665703133480.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uputregf</a><p>Copy a double-precision floating-point value into the specified general variable ($1 ... $99).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vdw1665703133550.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uputregs</a><p>Copy a string value to the specified general variable ($1 ... $99).</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533494\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533494\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "uputreg Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 04, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Copy a long integer value into the specified general variable ($1 ... $99). Explain this code long uputreg (shortregNbr, longvalue); Copy Parameters regNbr Number of the Uniface general variable; must be in the range 1 to 99. value Long integer value to put into the variable. Values can be from -2147483648 to 2147483647. Return Values The value of the value parameter. Use Library: yrtl Description uputreg copies the specified long integer value, which can range from -2147483648 to 2147483647 (or -231 to 231 -1), to the Uniface general variable (also known as dollar register) with the specified number regNbr , which can range from 1 to 99. There is no check on the validity of regNbr ; if it is out of range, a crash is likely to result. Explain this code #include <h3gl.h> EXPORT long putnum () { (void)uputreg(1, -2147483648); /* Lowest value possible */ } Copy Related Links ugetreg Get the integer value of a Uniface general variable ($1 ... $99). uputregf Copy a double-precision floating-point value into the specified general variable ($1 ... $99). uputregs Copy a string value to the specified general variable ($1 ... $99). Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}